summary: Changes your character\'s voice to cute asian voice
descriptionHtml:
Click the Video Tab to see the voice change

[youtube]BnI53hss6k0[/youtube] 




Changes your character\'s voice to cute asian voice

If you are not a big fan of animes, I suggest you to not install it

The voice is reaped from Continent Of the Ninth(KR)


-installation-

Place the folder on the fowllong directory

For steam user: C:\\Program Files\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\skyrim\\Data

For nonsteam users:  C:\\Program Files\\The Elder Scrolls Skyrim\\Data





-update-
added a non shouting words version (not the dragonshout)
